Enum AceEditorMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AceEditorMode>

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AceEditorMode>

    public enum AceEditorMode
extends java.lang.Enum<AceEditorMode>
    Enumeration for ACE editor modes. Note that the corresponding .js file must be loaded before a mode can be set.
